Title: De 7 dødssyndene
Director: Lars Gudmestad, Dag Johan Haugerud, Ørjan Karlsen
Writer: Harald Eia, Lars Gudmestad, Dag Johan Haugerud
Actors: Marit Andreassen, Petronella Barker, Egil Birkeland
Plot: Feature film length collection of seven short films about the biblical seven sins by preliminary younger Norwegian directors.
